<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM8.5">
<l>pārāḷum paṭarcelvam paratanampik kēyaruḷi</l>
<l>yārāvaṉ piḷaiyavaṉō ṭaruṅkāṉa maṭaintavaṉē</l>
<l>cīrāḷum varaimārpā tirukkaṇṇa purattaracē</l>
<l>tārāḷum nīṇmuṭiyeṉ ṟācaratī tālēlō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bestowing the expansive wealth of reigning over the earth on the noble Bharata himself,</l>
<l>O You, who reached the difficult forest with the younger brother</l>
<l rend="indent">[who bears You] love that is not satiated!</l>
<l>O You with a mountain[-like] chest reigned by excellence!</l>
<l>O King of Tirukaṇṇapuram! O my Dāśarathi with long hair reigned by a garland, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
